sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as Database<br/>JDBC TLS
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService<br/>80/443 mTLS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Kueue as Kueue API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMEval as LMEvalJob Pod<br/>gRPC/HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,HF: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>Bearer Token Auth
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, PVC<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>TrustyAI: Deploy TrustyAI Service
    TrustyAI->>DB: Initialize connection<br/>Username/Password + TLS verify-ca
    TrustyAI->>K8sAPI: Ready status

    Note over User,HF: Flow 2: Inference Monitoring

    KServe->>TrustyAI: Send inference data<br/>HTTP/HTTPS mTLS (Istio)
    TrustyAI->>DB: Store inference data<br/>JDBC TLS
    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: Scrape /q/metrics<br/>HTTP 8080
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: Metrics response

    Note over User,HF: Flow 3: LM Evaluation Job

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Bearer Token Auth
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event
    Operator->>Kueue: Submit Workload<br/>HTTPS ServiceAccount Token
    Kueue->>LMEval: Schedule Job Pod
    LMEval->>HF: Download model/dataset<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+ API Token
    LMEval->>KServe: Inference requests<br/>gRPC/HTTP TLS
    KServe-->>LMEval: Inference results
    LMEval->>K8sAPI: Update job status

    Note over User,HF: Flow 4: Guardrails Orchestration

    User->>K8sAPI: Create GuardrailsOrchestrator CR<br/>Bearer Token Auth
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch InferenceService<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create VirtualService/DestinationRule
    User->>KServe: Client request (via Guardrails)<br/>HTTPS TLS mTLS
    KServe->>TrustyAI: Detector inference<br/>HTTP/HTTPS mTLS
    TrustyAI-->>KServe: Detector result
    KServe->>KServe: LLM inference (if safe)
    KServe-->>User: Response
